Text Area 1:
Select the table and then use the advanced shape bar at the top of the canvas to:
Add rows and columns where you'd like using the insert options.
Delete specific rows and columns by selecting the row/column you want to remove and then using the delete options.
Click on a cell and add text to it by typing.
Select cells you would like to merge and then click "Merge" on the advanced shape bar at the top of the canvas.
To unmerge cells, click on the cell and then click "Unmerge" on the advanced shape bar.
Change the color of cells by selecting a cell(s) and then clicking "Fill Color"     on the properties bar.

Pro tip: Toggle the column and lane option on the advanced shape bar to quickly adjust your table.
